577@l>Line@nem>Line with No Emphasis@1@0@0@0@upcountry) was put in there, he exhibited a gentle annoyance. ‘The groans of
578@l>Line@nem>Line with No Emphasis@1@0@0@0@this sick person,’ he said, ‘distract my attention. And without that it is
