975@l>Line@nem>Line with No Emphasis@1@0@0@0@their imperfect manners, I suppose. This was the foreman—a boiler-maker by
976@l>Line@nem>Line with No Emphasis@1@0@0@0@trade—a good worker. He was a lank, bony, yellow-faced man, with big intense
