982@l>Line@nem>Line with No Emphasis@1@0@0@0@a connoisseur. He would rave about pigeons. After work hours he used sometimes
983@l>Line@nem>Line with No Emphasis@1@0@0@0@to come over from his hut for a talk about his children and his pigeons; at
