987@l>Line@nem>Line with No Emphasis@1@0@0@0@squatted on the bank rinsing that wrapper in the creek with great care, then
988@ll>Last Line@nem>Line with No Emphasis@1@0@0@0@spreading it solemnly on a bush to dry.
989@fl>First Line@nem>Line with No Emphasis@1@0@0@0@“I slapped him on the back and shouted, ‘We shall have rivets!’ He scrambled to
