992@l>Line@nem>Line with No Emphasis@1@0@0@0@finger to the side of my nose and nodded mysteriously. ‘Good for you!’ he cried,
993@l>Line@nem>Line with No Emphasis@1@0@0@0@snapped his fingers above his head, lifting one foot. I tried a jig. We capered
994@l>Line@nem>Line with No Emphasis@1@0@0@0@on the iron deck. A frightful clatter came out of that hulk, and the virgin
