996@l>Line@nem>Line with No Emphasis@1@0@0@0@sleeping station. It must have made some of the pilgrims sit up in their hovels.
997@l>Line@nem>Line with No Emphasis@1@0@0@0@A dark figure obscured the lighted doorway of the manager’s hut, vanished, then,
998@l>Line@nem>Line with No Emphasis@1@0@0@0@a second or so after, the doorway itself vanished, too. We stopped, and the
999@l>Line@nem>Line with No Emphasis@1@0@0@0@silence driven away by the stamping of our feet flowed back again from the
1000@l>Line@nem>Line with No Emphasis@1@0@0@0@recesses of the land. The great wall of vegetation, an exuberant and entangled
1001@l>Line@nem>Line with No Emphasis@1@0@0@0@mass of trunks, branches, leaves, boughs, festoons, motionless in the moonlight,
