1007@l>Line@nem>Line with No Emphasis@1@0@0@0@reasonable tone, ‘why shouldn’t we get the rivets?’ Why not, indeed! I did not
1008@l>Line@nem>Line with No Emphasis@1@0@0@0@know of any reason why we shouldn’t.  ‘They’ll come in three weeks,’ I said
1009@ll>Last Line@nem>Line with No Emphasis@1@0@0@0@confidently.
1010@fl>First Line@nem>Line with No Emphasis@1@0@0@0@“But they didn’t. Instead of rivets there came an invasion, an infliction, a
1011@l>Line@nem>Line with No Emphasis@1@0@0@0@visitation. It came in sections during the next three weeks, each section headed
