1026@l>Line@nem>Line with No Emphasis@1@0@0@0@intention in the whole batch of them, and they did not seem aware these things
1027@l>Line@nem>Line with No Emphasis@1@0@0@0@are wanted for the work of the world. To tear treasure out of the bowels of the
1028@l>Line@nem>Line with No Emphasis@1@0@0@0@land was their desire, with no more moral purpose at the back of it than there
