1039@l>Line@nem>Line with No Emphasis@1@0@0@0@thought to Kurtz. I wasn’t very interested in him. No. Still, I was curious to
1040@l>Line@nem>Line with No Emphasis@1@0@0@0@see whether this man, who had come out equipped with moral ideas of some sort,
1041@l>Line@nem>Line with No Emphasis@1@0@0@0@would climb to the top after all and how he would set about his work when
