1086@l>Line@nem>Line with No Emphasis@2@0@0@0@recovered imperfectly.... The two below me moved away then a few paces, and
1087@l>Line@nem>Line with No Emphasis@2@0@0@0@strolled back and forth at some little distance. I heard: ’Military
1088@l>Line@nem>Line with No Emphasis@2@0@0@0@post—doctor—two hundred miles—quite alone now—unavoidable delays—nine months—no
1089@l>Line@nem>Line with No Emphasis@2@0@0@0@news—strange rumours.’ They approached again, just as the manager was saying,
1090@l>Line@nem>Line with No Emphasis@2@0@0@0@‘No one, as far as I know, unless a species of wandering trader—a pestilential
1091@l>Line@nem>Line with No Emphasis@2@0@0@0@fellow, snapping ivory from the natives.’ Who was it they were talking about
1092@l>Line@nem>Line with No Emphasis@2@0@0@0@now? I gathered in snatches that this was some man supposed to be in Kurtz’s
1093@l>Line@nem>Line with No Emphasis@2@0@0@0@district, and of whom the manager did not approve. ‘We will not be free from
1094@l>Line@nem>Line with No Emphasis@2@0@0@0@unfair competition till one of these fellows is hanged for an example,’ he said.
1095@l>Line@nem>Line with No Emphasis@2@0@0@0@‘Certainly,’ grunted the other; ‘get him hanged! Why not? Anything—anything can
1096@l>Line@nem>Line with No Emphasis@2@0@0@0@be done in this country. That’s what I say; nobody here, you understand, _here_,
1097@l>Line@nem>Line with No Emphasis@2@0@0@0@can endanger your position. And why? You stand the climate—you outlast them all.
1098@l>Line@nem>Line with No Emphasis@2@0@0@0@The danger is in Europe; but there before I left I took care to—’ They moved off
1099@l>Line@nem>Line with No Emphasis@2@0@0@0@and whispered, then their voices rose again. ‘The extraordinary series of delays
1100@l>Line@nem>Line with No Emphasis@2@0@0@0@is not my fault. I did my best.’ The fat man sighed. ‘Very sad.’ ‘And the
