1122@fl>First Line@nem>Line with No Emphasis@2@0@0@0@“They swore aloud together—out of sheer fright, I believe—then pretending not to
1123@l>Line@nem>Line with No Emphasis@2@0@0@0@know anything of my existence, turned back to the station. The sun was low; and
1124@l>Line@nem>Line with No Emphasis@2@0@0@0@leaning forward side by side, they seemed to be tugging painfully uphill their
1125@l>Line@nem>Line with No Emphasis@2@0@0@0@two ridiculous shadows of unequal length, that trailed behind them slowly over
