1127@fl>First Line@nem>Line with No Emphasis@2@0@0@0@“In a few days the Eldorado Expedition went into the patient wilderness, that
1128@l>Line@nem>Line with No Emphasis@2@0@0@0@closed upon it as the sea closes over a diver. Long afterwards the news came
