1130@l>Line@nem>Line with No Emphasis@2@0@0@0@valuable animals. They, no doubt, like the rest of us, found what they deserved.
1131@l>Line@nem>Line with No Emphasis@2@0@0@0@I did not inquire. I was then rather excited at the prospect of meeting Kurtz
1132@l>Line@nem>Line with No Emphasis@2@0@0@0@very soon. When I say very soon I mean it comparatively.  It was just two months
1133@ll>Last Line@nem>Line with No Emphasis@2@0@0@0@from the day we left the creek when we came to the bank below Kurtz’s station.
1134@fl>First Line@nem>Line with No Emphasis@2@0@0@0@“Going up that river was like traveling back to the earliest beginnings of the
1135@l>Line@nem>Line with No Emphasis@2@0@0@0@world, when vegetation rioted on the earth and the big trees were kings. An
